cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.AI 

This paper discusses online machine learning algorithms for big data streams, which involves distributed data processing, online learning, and modeling methods. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DB (Databases). The paper also covers recommendation systems, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
